title: Tour bus crashes in Taiwan, at least 32 dead
text: Asia Pacific Tour bus crashes in Taiwan, at least 32 dead At least 32 people were killed and more were taken to hospital after a tour bus crashed on a highway in Taiwan on Tuesday night. Posted 14 Feb 2017 00:15 Updated 14 Feb 2017 00:28 The wreckage of a crashed bus is seen after an accident on a highway in Taipei, Taiwan February 13, 2017.
